from manim import *

class SpinningCube(Scene):
    def construct(self):
        # Create a 3D cube
        cube = Cube()
        cube.set_fill(BLUE, opacity=0.5)
        cube.set_stroke(BLUE_E, width=2)

        # Position cube at the center
        cube.move_to(ORIGIN)

        # Add cube to the scene
        self.add(cube)

        # Spin the cube smoothly over 5 seconds
        self.play(
            Rotate(cube, angle=2 * PI, axis=UP, run_time=5)
        )

        # Wait at the end
        self.wait()
